You nailed capturing the perfect mood with this theme! I imagine myself floating on the water of a hot spring near the peak of Mount Fuji. No extraneous noise or worries, just this music continuously looping. That would be true serenity.

Not only do you have great taste in VGM, but you also compose you own great VGM. Kudos, man! Do more OCs :)
